  "texts": [
    "In this paper, we will review the picking equipment from two aspects of mechanization and machine vision-based fruit picking technology, respectively, and analyze the structure, process, picking efficiency, fruit damage level, and picking environment of the equipment.",
    "Summarize the future development trend of automated picking equipment in order to promote the modernization of the fruit industry and the promotion of high technology as a reference.",
    "This review is organized as follows: Sect. 2 introduces mechanized fruit picking technologies, describing the characteristics and picking efficiency of seven picking technologies.",
    "Section 3 focuses on the principles and application status of machine vision-based picking technology and presents the current research status of automatic fruit picking equipment for apples, strawberries, tomatoes, citrus, and strawberries, respectively.",
    "In addition, agricultural drone fruit picking technology is introduced."
  ],
